noteText: Initial screening complete. Candidate has strong technical background with 8+ years experience. Excellent communication skills. Salary expectations within budget. Recommend proceeding to technical interview.
Technical interview feedback received. Candidate performed exceptionally well on coding challenges. Strong system design skills. Mark recommends moving to final round.
Candidate has excellent SAP BTP knowledge. Currently working at competitor company. Motivated by our company culture and growth opportunities.
Reference check completed. Previous manager gave excellent feedback. Described as reliable team player with strong technical skills.
Top candidate for Cloud Architect role. AWS certified with extensive Azure experience. Has led multiple enterprise migrations. Priority hire.
Panel interview completed. All interviewers gave highest ratings. CTO wants to make immediate offer before candidate is snapped up by competition.
Salary negotiation notes: Candidate expects $200K base + bonus. We offered $195K + 15% bonus + equity. Candidate requested time to consider.
Junior frontend developer with good React skills. Portfolio shows creative work. Needs mentorship but has high potential.
Note: Candidate missed initial phone screen. Rescheduled for next week. Follow up sent via email.
Excellent DevOps candidate. Strong Kubernetes expertise verified. Linux background is solid. Good cultural fit based on initial conversation.
Offer extended: $145K base + benefits. Candidate accepted! Start date confirmed for January 15th.
Candidate hired as Project Manager. Excellent performance throughout interview process. PMP certified with SAP implementation experience.
Onboarding completed successfully. Lisa has been assigned to the SAP SuccessFactors implementation project starting next month.
Backend skills are adequate but not exceptional. Other candidates showed stronger Java expertise. Moving to rejection.
Rejection email sent. Candidate was professional in response. May consider for future junior roles as skills develop.
UX Designer with strong Fiori experience. Portfolio demonstrates excellent attention to detail. Fluent in Spanish - could support LATAM clients.
Missed video interview on Dec 5th. Sent follow-up email to reschedule. Waiting for response.
DevOps candidate with solid Linux and automation background. Currently at fintech startup. Looking for more enterprise experience.
Business Analyst with SAP SuccessFactors specialization. Strong functional knowledge. Previous implementation experience at large enterprises.
Video interview scheduled with PM lead for next week. Candidate expressed strong interest in the project manager position.
